      "patch": "@@ -1,2 +1,11 @@\n # ToolPrivacyBench\n-Benchmarking purpose-bound privacy in tool-using LLM agents.\n+\n+This repository is the official repository for the paper:\n+\n+**ToolPrivacyBench: Benchmarking Purpose-Bound Privacy in Tool-Using LLM Agents**\n+\n+The code and benchmark data will be released upon acceptance or publication to support reproducibility and future research.\n+\n+## Status\n+\n+This repository is currently a placeholder. Code, benchmark data, evaluation scripts, and documentation will be made available after the publication process permits public release."
